=== Who Am I? === My name is Nikau, or Austin —honestly, either— and I'm a 23-year-old research fellow and consultant for mathematics and applications from New Zealand. I'm currently back home, but I typically reside in Vancouver, BC, Canada.
----
=== What, Actually, Is My Deal? === Wouldn't you like to know? Heck, ''I'd'' like to know... But if nothing else, I'm nicer than I seem. I have cyclothymia, three wonderful boyfriends, and I change the subject a lot.
==== No Really, It's Fine... I'm ''Fine'' ==== Nothing's really "fine," though, is it, ya know?
----
=== Wait, Does This Wiki Have the Math Extension?? === Oh gosh, I hope so...
My favourite integral right now is <math>\int_0^\infty e^{-x^2}\,\cos(x)\,dx</math>
